AGILE build environment

We need only 3 environment variable

- CFITSIO
- ROOTSYS
- AGILE=~/ADC/scientific_analysis

At the end we set

export PFILES=$AGILE/conf

To install the system

git clone git@github.com:AGILESCIENCE/BUILD_GRID_SCI_git.git
cd BUILD_GRID_SCI_git
sh download.sh
sh install.sh

To recompile the code
sh install.sh
